history.content:
Dinamic is a SAAS platform that helps small business sellers optimize how they market their e-commerce products. We help small businesses dynamically price their goods, manage their inventory, optimize their SEO, and launch effective ad campaigns regardless of the e-commerce platform they sell on. 

Dinamic has gotten accepted to Y-Combinator S22, Berkeley SkyDeck Accelerator, and the Soma Capital Fellowship. We are looking to hire software engineering, data engineering, and biz dev/marketing interns over the summer (flexible hours and start/end dates). Please reach out to vikram@dinamicpricing.com with any questions and drop your resume here: https://forms.gle/eebAUuSxHbN9uKwT8.
history.subject: Summer Internship Opportunity at Y-Combinator Accepted Berkeley Startup
